noria:TroubleTicket_CR01Outage noria:problemResponsibility <kos/TroubleTicket/problemResponsibility/ManagedBackboneNetworks> .

noria:TroubleTicket_WebsiteDown noria:troubleTicketCause "Database connection pool exhaustion."@en .
noria:TroubleTicket_WebsiteDown noria:problemResponsibility <kos/TroubleTicket/problemResponsibility/ContractApplicationHostingServices> .

